Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:37.50,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,LENGAN KANAN PENCURI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.12,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,VLAD III
